{"tid":2487995,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食肆僱員不打針恐遭炒魷  工會轟政府製勞資糾紛 業界寧維持現狀","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:48:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e1045b97bd35de678298c7b6ffd11e62e7249aaa","tid":2487995,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/ZNU6XRJASVFUVKLMJOMKALSNMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FZNU6XRJASVFUVKLMJOMKALSNMQ%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Ja0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=c117049f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FZNU6XRJASVFUVKLMJOMKALSNMQ%2F&h=637cd6da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/ZNU6XRJASVFUVKLMJOMKALSNMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n食肆僱員不打針恐遭炒魷 <br />\n工會轟政府製勞資糾紛 業界寧維持現狀<br />\n<br />\n【疫情何時了】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭硬推安心碼：羨慕人哋清零<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天才特首林鄭月娥提出「疫苗氣泡」防疫措施，若食肆等表列處所要放寬營業限制，員工必須接種疫苗。多個勞工團體批評，要求員工打針非合理工作指令，憂慮若員工以懷孕或長期病患等理由拒絕，會遭炒魷。有勞工團體一日內已收到十多宗求助，料會引發勞資糾紛，炮轟政府「帶頭搞事」。有連鎖餐飲集團拒絕就範，寧願維持現有堂食的防疫安排，亦不欲逼員工及顧客打針。<br />\n<br />\n本報向勞工處查詢，若有員工因拒絕接種而遭解僱或被迫放無薪假等，僱主是否違法？處方未能提供清晰答案，僅稱《僱傭條例。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：食客分兩區 專家轟政府妄想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZD7UUAn2bbETbEyb_TygU9injo0=/510x377/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRCYPZHLFNFX7GWN36VFN3YZ3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZD7UUAn2bbETbEyb_TygU9injo0%3D%2F510x377%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRCYPZHLFNFX7GWN36VFN3YZ3I.jpg&h=7ee40aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■政府提出食肆員工須接種疫苗，才放寬營業限制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n員工欲懷孕 或無證明文件<br />\n<br />\n職工盟總幹事蒙兆達指出，要求員工接種非合理工作指令，若員工因不想、懷孕、長期病患等原因拒絕而遭解僱，屬無理解僱。在現行法例下，除非是懷孕、無薪假期間被解僱等可復職，否則只有待通知金和年資補償。不過，若員工聽從僱主建議，打針後產生嚴重副作用，「係咪屬工傷？問題令人擔憂，因有保險公司話打疫苗後副作用未必包」，他批評勞工處在有關方面含糊其辭，期望清晰交代。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟一日內已收到十多宗求助，「飲食業首當其衝，有老闆或經理叫員工幫。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟零售、商業及成衣業總工會總幹事張麗霞亦指出，懷孕或正在餵哺母乳，又或準備懷孕的員工對接種疫苗有憂慮，「如果唔。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n叙福樓集團主席、稻苗學會會長黃傑龍表示，政府提出的「疫苗氣泡」防疫措施，「只係對老闆有誘因，員工係零誘因」，不認同以。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VdxnYW3DGfy92ma9CRmqY2VJMp4=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EM2CI45JLFD5LFDEGI3MSH3524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVdxnYW3DGfy92ma9CRmqY2VJMp4%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEM2CI45JLFD5LFDEGI3MSH3524.jpg&h=23be7d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張麗霞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林瑞華稱針後出事孭唔起<br />\n<br />\n香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華亦表示，不會要求員工一定要打針，「條命係佢，如果佢有事，我負唔起咁大責任」，他相信業界不會為求生意額而要員工打針。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局長陳肇始昨於電台節目表示，會在本周約見飲食業界商討「疫苗氣泡」放寬社交距離的執行細節，包括如何處理不接種疫苗的員工和顧客安排。她聲稱新措施是為業界放寬營。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qM0WeXXFL0P92jCOCgHXdYAk-uA=/510x237/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z3AFCLOFEFGHFO4OFH6H3KZNLQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqM0WeXXFL0P92jCOCgHXdYAk-uA%3D%2F510x237%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ3AFCLOFEFGHFO4OFH6H3KZNLQ.gif&h=2818ea3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f129f5fc858c5cd1ba070e5eb6a2ac3a685ebf8b","tid":2487995,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"炒人唔洗賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1f2a56d81ab0119f461b5b4aca68e9424deaa1","tid":2487995,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"monkey同埋腥港個